### Form States

```tsx
// Default input
<TextInput
  className="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-text"
  placeholderTextColor="rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.6)"
/>

// Focused input
<TextInput
  className={twMerge(
    "bg-surface border rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-text",
    isFocused ? "border-primary" : "border-border"
  )}
